REM Title: Matrix rain (cmatrix)
REM Author: Cypher
REM Description: Opens Terminal fullscreen and runs cmatrix. Falls back to a
REM Perl one-liner if cmatrix isn't installed.
REM Target: macOS (cmatrix optional via `brew install cmatrix`)
DELAY 500
GUI SPACE
DELAY 500
STRING Terminal
DELAY 1000
ENTER
DELAY 800
CTRL GUI f
DELAY 500
STRING cmatrix 2>/dev/null || perl -e 'while(1){print chr(33+int(rand(94)));select(undef,undef,undef,0.003)}'
ENTER
